<p class="">Several messages are being sent to France in the course of the day, but the question whether one should be transmitted from the House of Commons, or I presume from the Houses of Parliament, is one that I should like to discuss with my colleagues.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
